AI Studio Licensing Policy (Dual License: Community & Commercial)

AI Studio is released under a dual-license model: the AI Studio Community License (free) and a Commercial License (paid).

1. AI Studio Community License

Permitted Uses (Free):

Individuals (Personal Use):

Granted a free, perpetual license to use all standard AI Studio functions.

Content created using AI Studio may be used for personal or commercial projects.

Organizations (Limited Use):

Organizations may use AI Studio only in its standard, unmodified, out-of-the-box form for evaluation or non-commercial purposes.

Strictly Prohibited Without a Commercial License:

Team Deployment: Installing, hosting, or operating AI Studio for simultaneous use by multiple users in an organization (e.g., on shared servers, internal networks, or private clouds).

Code Modification or Derivative Works: Modifying, translating, reverse-engineering, or creating derivative products based on AI Studio source code.

Redistribution: Redistributing AI Studio (modified or unmodified) as part of another product or service.

Competitive Offering: Using AI Studio (in whole or in part) as the foundation of a competing commercial product.

2. Commercial License

A Commercial License is REQUIRED for any of the following:

Internal multi-user or team deployment.

Any secondary development, customization, or modification of the source code.

Embedding or redistributing AI Studio as part of your own commercial offering.

Access to official technical support, warranties, or indemnification.

A Commercial License grants you the legal right to use AI Studio for enterprise purposes and to adapt its source code for your organization’s needs.

👉 To obtain a Commercial License, please contact: aifoxdw@gmail.com

3. Contributions

By submitting contributions, you agree to grant the AI Studio maintainers a perpetual, worldwide, royalty-free, irrevocable license to use, modify, and sublicense your contributions under both the Community and Commercial Licenses.

4. Trademarks & UI

The AI Studio name, logo, and visual/interaction design are protected intellectual property and trademarks.

You may not use AI Studio branding, trademarks, or UI/UX designs for derivative or resale products without explicit permission.

